<div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-charity-pages" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-charity-pages-list">
    
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <i class="fab fa-internet-explorer"></i>
        Charity pages
        <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#charityPagesHelpFull" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="charityPagesHelpFull"><i class="far fa-question-circle"></i></a>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col">
            <div class="collapse text-muted" id="charityPagesHelpFull">
              <div class="card card-body mb-3">
              When all your charity details have been added, and you have put your charity 'online',
              your charity becomes visible on this website. Volunteers can find your charity on the explore
              page, and when they click on your charity they will be directed to the mining-donations page. 
              You can view both of these pages directly below. Note that on the
              donations page you can download the CoinFunnel mining application, just as your 
              volunteers would. Feel free to try it out.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row pb-1">
          <div class="col text-center">
            <h5>Explore page</h5>
          </div>
          <div class="col text-center">
            <h5 class="mb-0">Donation page</h5>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col text-center">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body text-center" style="padding-top: 5em; padding-bottom: 5em;">
                <% if (locals.cause.isOnline) { %>
                  <a class="card-title" 
                    href="<%= `${inject.ACL.GetExplore.resource}?keyword=${encodeURIComponent(locals.cause.name)}` %>"><i class="fas fa-search fa-3x"></i></a>
                <% } else { %>
                  <a tabindex="0" 
                    data-toggle="popover" 
                    data-placement="top" 
                    data-trigger="focus" 
                    data-content="Your charity is not currently online, and so is not visible on the Explore page." 
                    class="popover-links" 
                    href="#"><i class="fas fa-search fa-3x"></i></a>
                <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col text-center">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body text-center" style="padding-top: 5em; padding-bottom: 5em;">
                <% if (locals.cause.isOnline) { %>
                  <a id="view-showcase-link"
                    href="<%= `${inject.ACL.GetShowcase.resource}/${locals.cause.path.getCombinedPath()}` %>"><i class="fas fa-donate fa-3x"></i></a>
                <% } else { %>
                  <a tabindex="0" 
                    data-toggle="popover" 
                    data-placement="top" 
                    data-trigger="focus" 
                    data-content="Your charity is not currently online, and so is not visible on the Donation page." 
                    class="popover-links" 
                    href="#"><i class="fas fa-donate fa-3x"></i></a>
                <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
